name: Social Circles
body:
### Welcome to Social Circles
Social Circles aims to be a powerful, elegant Web application that allows people to visualize their social connections and gain key analytical insight into their friend networks.

### Contributors
Social Circles is a project by Jimmy Wu (@jimmywu126) at UC Berkeley and Jimmy Nonno (@jnonno) at UC San Diego, currently studying abroad at Yonsei University in South Korea.
